name: Utz Cheese Balls Barrel, Tasty Snack Baked with Real Cheddar Cheese, Delightfully Poppable Party Snack, Gluten, Cholesterol and Trans-Fat Free, Kosher Certified, 36.5 Oz
short_description: CHEESY AND CRUNCHY – When you taste the pairing of tangy cheddar flavor and a satisfying crunch, you’ll never want to put this barrel of Utz Cheese Balls down. These crunchy, munchy cheese balls are finger-licking fun.

PARTY SNACKS – So poppable and delicious, these crunchy cheese balls are the perfect party snack. Our largest size cheese ball barrel is perfect for parties or families with big snackers—all you have to do is put it in a bowl and serve, or enjoy right out of the barrel!

RESEALABLE CONTAINER – Utz Cheese Balls come in a conveniently resealable plastic 36.5 oz. barrel, so you can order in bulk and snack as you please. Just snap the cap back on tightly to maintain freshness.
GLUTEN FREE – Enjoy these delicious, crunchy cheese balls without the guilt. They are cooked without hydrogenated oils and are gluten, cholesterol, and trans-fat free. Kosher certified.

WE ARE UTZ – Since 1921, Utz has been making and selling quality pretzels and other delicious snacks in Hanover, PA, the snack capital of the world! The Utz Team works hard each day by bringing family crafted flavor in our world-class snacks. As a result, our snacks are crunchier, lighter, and fresher earning Utz smiles on the faces of generation after generation.
product_description: Don’t settle for any old cheese puff when you can have a barrel of Utz Cheese Balls and get that delectable taste of real cheddar cheese that you crave! When you taste the pairing of tangy cheddar flavor and a satisfying crunch, you’ll never want to put this 36.5 oz. barrel of delightfully poppable cheese balls down. Whether you’re lounging on the couch or hosting a party, Utz Cheese Balls are the perfect party snack. Our largest size cheese ball barrel is perfect for parties or families with big snackers—all you have to do is put it in a bowl and serve or enjoy right out of the barrel! Plus, the conveniently resealable container allows you to share with everyone—or not—then reseal the container to keep any extras fresh. Enjoy these delicious, crunchy cheese balls without the guilt. Not only are they kosher certified, but they are cooked without hydrogenated oils and are gluten, cholesterol and trans-fat free. With simple ingredients, Utz uses a baking process that ensures that you get the freshest, crispiest crunch you crave! The Utz story began in Hanover, Pennsylvania, in a small-town kitchen. It was 1921. Bill and Salie Utz thought potato chips could be better. They believed potato chips should be made from clean, simple ingredients that should be minimally processed to bring out the natural flavor of farm-fresh potatoes. Over the next 100 years and more, we’ve added pretzels, cheese, popcorn, pork rinds and other delicious snack foods. Headquartered in Hanover, Pennsylvania and with fifteen manufacturing facilities conveniently located across the United States, the Utz Team works hard each day to honor Bill and Salie Utz’s legacy by bringing family crafted flavor in our world-class snacks. As a result, our snacks are crunchier, lighter, and fresher earning Utz smiles on the faces of generation after generation.
